name: Nolie - Interlude For An Average Joe (Clear Eyes Remix)

attributes.trait_type: Interlude For An Average Joe (Clear Eyes Remix)

metadata.description:
Nolie & Clear Eyes (Jeremy Lloyd) have been working alongside one another creatively since they met in a session in 2016.
 
After spending a few years documenting Jeremy and his musical endeavors around the world (a notable collab being the music video Nolie filmed for Clear Eyes ft. Reo Cragun - "No Place I'd Rather Be" in 2021) - Nolie decided to make the transition in 2019 to begin releasing his own music with help and support from artists and close friends Slenderbodies & Clear Eyes.  

Now multiple years and songs later we are seeing the first remix of a Nolie track - and no better artist to do this than the masterful 
Clear Eyes <3
